title: Mr. Azaad
subTitle: Azaad, an orphan, takes to petty crime and acts like a modern-day Robin Hood. However, the death of an honest constable causes him to take stock of his actions.

title: Kasak
subTitle: Divya, a young woman, loves Suraj, who dies an untimely death. She is soon forced to marry Vijay due to familial pressure but demands that he divorce her.

title: China Town
subTitle: Raised by different parents, identical twins, Shekhar and Mike become a singer and a gangster in ChinaTown, respectively. But, their paths intersect when the police make Shekhar impersonate Mike.

title: Comedy Station
subTitle: Various talented comedians perform hilarious skits and stand-up acts on diverse themes and topics to entertain the audience.

title: Vaastu Shastra
subTitle: A couple and their sister move to their new house with their young son, but soon discover that an old tree outside the house holds a strange curse which is haunting their house.

title: Dil Hai Ke Manta Nahin
subTitle: When Pooja flees from home to reunite with her boyfriend, she meets Raghu, who agrees to escort her. As they travel together, she subsequently catches feelings for him.

title: Har Dil Jo Pyar Karega
subTitle: Raj, an aspiring singer, rescues Pooja, the daughter of a wealthy man, from an accident. However, he soon finds himself in a web of complications when he falls in love with her best friend.

title: Raaz
subTitle: Sanjana and Aditya go to Ooty for a holiday to save their unsteady marriage. However, she is haunted by a spirit who reveals some dark secrets about her husband and his past.

title: Kshatriya
subTitle: Two royal families in Rajasthan fight annually to fulfil an age-old tradition. Unaware of the clash, their grandsons become best friends and attempt to end the family feud.

title: Gair
subTitle: Vijay falls for Madhu and wishes to marry her. However, things take a turn when Raja, Vijay's step-brother, attempts to destroy their relationship.

title: Virasat
subTitle: Shakti visits home and hopes to return soon. But when his village is torn in a feudal war due to his warring cousins, he is forced to take up his father's legacy, even at the cost of his own dreams.

title: Aashiq Hoon Baharon Ka
subTitle: Chaos ensues as Vikram, driven by greed and ego, hinders the blossoming romance between Ashok and Veera by trapping Ashok with false accusations of theft.

title: Phagun
subTitle: Shanta Damle, who is unable to live alone after her daughter's marriage, moves in with her, much to the displeasure of Suman, her son-in-law, who detests her when he learns her motive.

title: Toxic Shark
subTitle: When a group's short getaway coincides with the hunting season of acid-shooting poisonous sharks, their trip turns into a nightmare as they struggle to survive.

title: Chacha Bhatija
subTitle: Teja, a widower, marries Sonia, a girl who only wants to get her hands on his inheritance. So, she creates animosity between Teja, his brother and his son.

title: Naya Raasta
subTitle: Chander, a criminal lawyer, gives up his successful career and returns to his village. However, things take a turn as he comes face-to-face with various social problems.

title: Aa Gale Lag Jaa
subTitle: Prem, a young man, must part from his lover Preeti even though she is pregnant. Years later, they reunite, but Preeti is about to engage another man.

title: Yakeen
subTitle: When a couple meets with a car accident, the husband injures his head and loses his memory. After finding some evidence, he grows suspicious of everyone around him, including his wife.

title: Amar Prem
subTitle: Nandkishore Sharma alias Nandu is born in the Sharma family. His mother tragically passes away, leaving him in the care of his father who decides to re-marry a woman named Kamla. Kamla is not very kind to.

title: Izzat
subTitle: A man sets out to avenge his late mother, who was molested and abandoned by his biological father. He finds history repeating itself when he sees his half-brother following in his father's footsteps.

title: Dildaar
subTitle: Banke, a farmer, falls in love with the village headman's daughter. However, when he is rejected, he vows to marry a woman better than the headman's daughter.

title: Amar Deep
subTitle: Raja, an arrogant man, is in love with his servant's daughter, Radha. He is enraged to find that she loves Kishan, so he hatches a devious plan to get them married and then keep them apart.

title: Ab Tak Chhappan
subTitle: Sadhu, a high-ranking policeman, confronts departmental deceit and the tragedy of losing his spouse. Pushed to the edge, he decides to fight crime his own way, ignoring the rules to seek justice.

title: Tejasvini
subTitle: Lala Khurana, a mafia leader, tries to quash the charges of molestation against his son and make him the CM. However, ASP Tejasvini is hell-bent on ending their tyranny and getting them convicted.

title: Isi Ka Naam Zindagi
subTitle: A kind-hearted zamindar donates a plot of land to the elderly Bansiram. After the zamindar's death, his lecherous son Devraj tries to reacquire the land at any cost.

title: Anari
subTitle: Rama, a simpleton, is appointed as the bodyguard of Rajnandini, a rich girl. She soon falls in love with him but her brothers' violent nature gets in the way of her uniting with Rama.

title: Jawani Zindabad
subTitle: Shashi gets his sister married to Ravi without offering dowry in order to take a stand against the practice. However, he gets harassed by his sister's in-laws for his stance.

title: Junoon
subTitle: Vikram is badly injured and his friend is killed by a cursed tiger. He soon learns that the curse has been passed onto him and he will turn into a tiger on a full moon night.

title: Bade Ghar Ki Beti
subTitle: Mala, a poor girl, marries the son of her father's employer. Things, however, take a turn for the worse when her father-in-law dies and his ruthless children show their true colours.

title: Shola Aur Shabnam
subTitle: Divya loves Karan and plans to get married to him. However, a notorious gangster's brother, Bali, who also has his eyes on her, goes to great lengths to destroy her relationship with Karan.
